title: Looking for ranked team(OCE)
body: Hello I m looking to join a ranked team at gold/silver level. I main support but can pretty much play most roles, i can play every day of the week and some weekend nights/ due to work. I am currently in Gold 5.

replies.body: Hey, my team has been having issues with our ADC not being able to practice with us as much as we would like, if you are interested you can join and play in a tournament on sunday March 12th with us, as of right now we have 2 silver and one platinum in our team.
